QuestData.Title: Helm's Deep
QuestData.Description: This helm and its associated components are marked with the seal of Stormwind. It was no doubt cast off from an Alliance ship that suffered a similar fate to yours.$b$bLooking closer, this seems far too intricate and sturdy to be everyday diving equipment. Perhaps Nazgrim can make some sense of this...
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Alliance S.E.A.L. Equipment to Legionnaire Nazgrim at The Immortal Coil.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak to Legionnaire Nazgrim at The Immortal Coil.
